editorialNotes.standard: Great apps let us do things we couldn’t before. With its phenomenally detailed 3D models, this Apple Design Award winner is a groundbreaking tool for exploring the human body. It’s changed how students learn and given doctors a powerful new way to discuss patients’ conditions. Whether you’re studying the circulatory system or cutting through muscles with Apple Pencil, the technology’s astounding.
